-- Romanian Court Upholds Referendum Extended Hours, Mediafax Says
-- B y   I r i n a   S a v u
-- 2012-07-24T14:35:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-24/romanian-court-upholds-referendum-extended-hours-mediafax-says.html
Romania’s Constitutional Court
upheld today a voting-hours extension at the presidential
impeachment referendum on July 29, news service Mediafax
 reported today .  The court said the Parliament change to a referendum law
that lengthened voting times by four extra hours was
constitutional, after debating the challenges submitted by the
opposition last week, the Bucharest-based  news agency  said
today, citing the court’s ruling.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Irina Savu in Bucharest at 
 isavu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
